parameters:
There are some characters engraved on the door
that doesn't seem to open...
\nw[\N[21]]Can you read this, Prae?
\nw[\N[21]]No way, you collapsed again...!?

\nw[Shia]Calm down, Prae is always doing farm work and
carrying a communication device. She's not
constantly watching us or anything.
\nw[\N[21]]Ah, I see... now that you mention it...

\nw[\N[21]]I hired a caretaker before going out, and even if
she collapses, she should be taken to the
clinic...
\nw[Shia]Ah, you're worrying too much.

\nw[\N[21]]However, what should we do? Only Prae can read the
demon language.

\nw[Shia]Ah, what's going on? What exactly are these demon
characters? Are they different from the magic
characters?
\nw[\N[21]]Well, I don't know the details, but...
\nw[Shia]Whoa, what is this!? Is it fog!?
\nw[\N[21]]Ugh, I can't see ahead!?
\nw[Shia]Hey, don't touch me... Ahh!?
\nw[\N[21]]Shia!? Ah, my body feels numb...
\nw[Dalton]What's this, my body is moving on its own...!?
\nw[Shia]What the hell are you doing... stop...
\nw[Shia]Ah, you're worrying too much.

\nw[\N[21]]Shia? Suddenly, it feels like your voice has
become distant...
\nw[Dalton]Sorry, my body is moving on its own...!
\nw[\N[1]]Wait, this sound...!

\nw[\N[21]]Damn, I can't see anything because of the fog, but
this sound...

\nw[\N[21]]Ugh, I can't move...! Is there anyone who can
move!?
\nw[\N[1]]I'm also feeling numb...
\nw[\N[3]]I'm sorry, I'm also feeling numb.
\nw[Fross]It's the same... I'm sorry.
\nw[Saria]I'm pathetic...
\nw[Thorz]Ah, I can't move.
\nw[Huma]Haha, I can't move.

\nw[Dalton]Rather, moving on its own... hah, hah, it feels
good!

\nw[\N[21]]...Everyone's here! It's only natural since we
were close by...
\nw[\N[21]]Damn, what should I do...
\nw[Uka]...Can you... move...?
\nw[\N[21]]Seriously!?
\nw[Uka]......Seriously......
\nw[\N[21]]Well then, can't we dispel the fog?
\nw[Uka]......Yeah...... Let's give it a try......
\nw[\N[21]]Oh, it's a bit thin...?
\nw[\N[21]]The fog is clearing...
\nw[\N[21]]What the hell are you doing, Dalton!?

\nw[Dalton]No, my body won't listen... Ahh, it feels too
good...!
\nw[\N[21]]Hey, is Shia okay buried in the wall like that?

\nw[Dalton]I can barely hear her voice, but it seems like
she's okay. However, it looks like something was
shoved into her mouth...
\nw[\N[21]]Oh, right now only Uka can move. Can you stop her?
\nw[Uka]...Stop...? It feels... good...
\nw[\N[21]]No, this situation is...
\nw[Prae's voice]Huh? What is this situation?

\nw[\N[21]]Prae, huh? Perfect timing. Something like gas or
something has made us unable to move, and Shia is
being violated by Dalton... Do you know anything
about this situation?

\nw[Prae's voice]Mmm, being embedded in the wall... Ahh, it's not a
trap of the erotic dungeon.
\nw[\N[21]]No, I understand that but...

\nw[Prae's voice]Because there is a numbing atmosphere drifting
ahead, we need to neutralize it. For that purpose,
a pair of a man and a woman must continue to
engage in sexual activity and continuously
generate magical power.

\nw[Prae's voice]It seems like the dungeon has arbitrarily decided
on a pair. The others can proceed ahead.
\nw[\N[21]]Seriously... leaving her like that...

\nw[Prae's voice]It's impossible. Since we couldn't break down the
door, the strength is probably the same. Shia
won't be able to escape without achieving the
objective.

\nw[Prae's voice]And without neutralizing it, we won't be able to
move from there...
\nw[Prae's voice]Hmm? Isn't Uka the only one not moving?
\nw[Prae's voice]Well... well, I suppose it's fine.

\nw[Prae's voice]In order to recover from numbness, we need magical
power. Don't wait for too long.
\nw[\N[21]]Ugh... I guess there's no other choice...

\nw[Prae's voice]I don't think any monsters will come there, but
Uka, please stay on guard.
\nw[Uka]......Yeah......I got it......
\nw[Dalton]Huh? Shia's condition... What is this!?
\nw[\N[21]]What's wrong?
\nw[Dalton]Shia is going to give birth... Ugh, my body...!
\nw[\N[21]]Huh? Giving birth...

\nw[Prae's voice]There seems to be a birthing ritual. It's similar
to that one.

\nw[Prae's voice]If there is a large amount of magical power, we
can make her give birth immediately...

\nw[\N[21]]Whoa, she's really giving birth...!? Is it okay to
do it in a place like this!?

\nw[Prae's voice]It's similar to the birthing ritual, so it should
be fine. Well, we can't just leave her alone...
Uka, could you bring the baby to the surface?
\nw[Uka]......Yeah......I got it......
A
\nw[\N[21]]Are you able to move without any problems...?

\nw[\N[21]]Dalton, I'm going now, so please tell Shia I said
hello.

\nw[Dalton]Oh, I see... It's tough for an old person like me
to have my body moved without rest...
<ActiveMessage:Haa,_haa,_amazing!>

\nw[Dalton]*panting* My body moves on its own...! It feels
too good, it's becoming addictive...!
\nw[\N[21]](I'm not sure about Shia, but we should hurry...)
